  <para>
    The <classname>OrientationMapDisplay</classname> draws each pixel
    in a &micro;, colored according to the &micro;'s <link
    linkend="Section-Concepts-Microstructure-OrientationMap"><classname>Orientation
    Map</classname></link>.  The <varname>colorscheme</varname>
    parameter describes how the orientation angles are to be converted
    to colors for the display.
  </para>

  <para>
    The <classname>OrientationMapDisplay</classname> displays
    orientations even if they are not actually used in any of the
    &materials; in the &micro;.
  </para>

